        "description": "Prison Boss VR is a crafting and simulation game with one simple goal: make cash! Locked up in your prison cell, produce and sell contraband items to buy your freedom back. But don’t get caught by the guards!\n\nCrafting at night…\nRoll cigarettes, fill up bottles, write erotic letters, and more! Be sure to stash your goods well, or they will be seized by the patrolling guards! \n\n…Trading during the day\nSell all the products of your hard illegal work to your fellow inmates. You can also use them to complete special jobs to earn reputation along with useful rewards!\n\nKey Features: \n•  Unlock 11 craftable items\n•  Complete 80 jobs across 4 different prisons\n•  Play the game in Story, Arcade or Boss mode\n•  Customize your cell by adding new furniture\n•  Adapt your cell to the size of your VR playspace\n•  Jazz along our awesome soundtrack\n•  Make mama proud\n\nBut most importantly, become the Prison Boss and get your way out of this hole! ",
